Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.23,0:02:52.96,opCbig5,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}今亦得見
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.21,0:02:58.53,opCbig5,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}逆風疾走 趕上電車
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.09,0:03:01.52,opCbig5,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}蕙芷芬芳 色狀霓虹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.17,0:03:04.72,opCbig5,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}向陽步道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.02,0:03:09.81,opCbig5,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}鹿撞愈疾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.37,0:03:16.94,opCbig5,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}散學廊下 鐘聲迴響
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.38,0:03:20.34,opCbig5,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}無奇世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.34,0:03:24.75,opCbig5,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}漸始閃光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.97,0:03:31.47,opCbig5,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}走而出者 慕君之思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.92,0:03:37.48,opCbig5,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}眼底心內 如系如縛
